e universe. Peace!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/5TkiAoe</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[sharperimage]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Men are NOT becoming more conservative</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/pudl7bJ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bgMYvT8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Headlines claim a new study was released saying that GenZ men are becoming much more conservative than women.

Issues with the "study"?
1. Online respondents via webpage form, no effort to remove botnet or multiple replies

2. Biased wording of questions 

3. Insufficient responses from some countries to provide accurate statistical analysis where study claims definitive results

4. Study summary claims "both men & women are becoming more conservative but men are changing at a faster rate"; published data shows both are becoming more LIBERAL.

5. Study summary claims conservatism by men and women is being led by an increase in active religion among Gen Z. There are literally no questions within the study about religion so even if the rest of the study were accurate it would be impossible to tell if religion was a factor.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/pudl7bJ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[meauho]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>D'Oh!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/IXr6Zol</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wAnTnt4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/IXr6Zol</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[PatThaiCM]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Celebrities and their ages</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/BSX70US</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PBNrhy9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>18 year old Britney Spears in 1999</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gMKZuWc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>24 year old Cameron Diaz in 1996</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AVPguLl.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>20 year old Drew Barrymore in 1995</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9S7QwMt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>19 year old Tyra Banks in 1993</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QzJuJWp.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>30 year old Meryl Streep in 1979</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YDITMEB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>25 year old Audrey Hepburn in 1954</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cJ29sKV.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>16 year old Elizabeth T