t: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I don't know what I did to please the old gods but it happened again, found a PS4 in a paper bag on the ground in another recycling room at work today. I was about to throw it in the bin when I felt the weight and shape, excepted it to be a DVD player or something that a tenant was too lazy to put in the electric waste room.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Dg2CRtg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Friend loaned me his PS4 controller and power cable to test it out. Unlike the PS1 this one didn't work.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dFymMMX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Luna identified the problem (the error code helped too), the hard-drive was busted.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PcdPaqW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Got a new one for 250 Riksdaler (ca 25usd)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3i6zLyg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And just like that, I'll finally be able to play Bloodborne after all these years.

Bonus: a coworker told me he found a couple PS2 controllers a few weeks ago in the same area. We don't know who's throwing this stuff away but we're not gonna stop 'em.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/IDxYdRx</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[AllMaktAtTengilVarBefriare]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>You cannot reason with a cult</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/DBwd5Bs</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/aaNjzy1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/DBwd5Bs</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[godofhorizons]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Real head scratcher</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/TxDvvZH</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WjfpZiJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/TxDvvZH</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[malbec]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The cellos. They need to be louder.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/9vx0Cj9</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Q1rkRrc.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/9vx0Cj9</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Iwokeupdeadthismorning]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Peak dumbassery</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/9Uh4mYM</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GDSqdrz.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/9Uh4mYM</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Rainbowdaesh]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>A moderately sized DK dump of stolen memes for these trying times 1322.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/2PUNMIZ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uwo0eHP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><s